data.description: Can You Say Barndominium With A Pool on 2 Acres.  This one is spacious at 3360 sq ft, Chefs dream in this large kitchen, quartz countertops, SS appliances, walk in pantry, and an island with storage.  Open concept to dining and living area with gas log fireplace.  Large primary bedroom with nice size bath featuring separate vanities, jetted tub, walk in shower, tile flooring, and good size walk in closet. Guest rooms good size, one with barn door adjoining living area for office, secondary living, or game room, plus one with built ins for additional storage. Huge insulated garage approx 1800 sq ft with partial floored storage above, and two 14' overhead commercial doors, 220 electric for RV.  Screened in porch overlooking the heated in ground gunite pool with slide for lots of summer fun.  Property has a detached storage/office building, two 2 car carports, and 2 smaller storage buildings.  Wooded area at back of property for your imagination.  Very private setting with lots of room, come make it yours.
